data.text:
@danneybee Hello. We seem to have some problems with the website at this moment. I recommend that you try to book the flights again later - or if it's urgent you can call our phone support for help. Numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Daniel_AvOr Hello, only our phone support are able to assist with making reservations but if you are able to book the flights on our website you can do so and then contact us via live-chat with your booking reference to reserve space for your pet.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Lothian27 Hi. There seem to be some issues with the website currently, if you need help with booking or rebooking tickets I recommend that you call our phone service for assistance. Phone numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@SunnaGunnlaugs Hello, I'm sorry to hear that your flight is cancelled. If you cannot find new alternatives using the website you have to call our phone support for assistance with rebooking. Phone numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@easytigerlily Hello, we have responded to your other tweet.

Best regards,
Anton.

@dottyslipper Hello! At the moment we have no information about when direct flights MAN to OSL will resume but I recommend you to regularly check our website using the low fare price calender, you can then tick the box to check for direct flights only.

Best regards,
Anton.

@dottyslipper Hello! You can see the availability for direct flights MAN to OSL at our website by using the lowest fare calendar and then you tick the box "Direct flights only".

Best regards,
Anton.

@thitrieu52 Hi, if you are unhappy with what Customer Service can offer you, please contact our Customer Care department directly: https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh
Please choose: Booking/Refund and Sales services &gt; Refund or SAS Travel Voucher &gt; SAS Travel Voucher
Kind regards, Rebecka

@megan_cresswell Hi ! 
If you contact us on Messenger or our Live chat, we will help you check which flights are available.
With kind regards Liv.

@TCStJWarrington Hello, we apologize for the inconvenience experienced during check-in. If you wish to send us feedback regarding this we recommend that you use our feedback-form https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Best regards,
Anton.

@RussianVillain Hello, please contact us via live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your booking details and we can help you add VLML meal.

Best regards,
Anton.

@AlexBerg1 Hej, i det här fallet behöver du hämta boardingkortet på flygplatsen. Om du är svensk medborgare behöver du inget negativt test för att resa till Sverige men du kan behöva styrka ditt medborgarskap på flygplatsen före avresa.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@Quak3r72 Hello
SAS as an airline does not require a test for the traveler to travel with us, but the staff at the gate will check your travel documents and any test if the country you are traveling to requires this. 

Kind regards, Anja!

@Yueyueadventure Hi!

Yes you should get an extra bag if you are a Star Alliance gold member, So you should have two bags included in your ticket and one extra for your Star Alliance card, but the non members don't get an extra bag.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@siv2000 Hello, 
I will refer you to call our ticket office, then my colleagues on the phone can help you rebook your tickets. https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj. I recommend calling in the morning for reduced queue time.  https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj 

Kind regards, Anja!

@torhovland Hej, det är bra om du har all dokumentation som krävs för att resa under hela din resa. Du kan se vilka regler som gäller för din resa här: https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De
Har du fler frågor rekommenderar vi att du kollar med de Norska myndigheterna.
Vänliga hälsningar, Rebecka

@Laura36431495 I'm sorry to hear that you were not informed of the change of your flight. If you want to find alternatives for your flight you can call our support here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
You can also submit a claim with our Customer Care: https://t.co/OzrIxYNv63
Kind regards, Rebecka

@hannafia Hej, vänligen kolla så att du inte har någon VPN eller företagsbrandvägg aktiverad på din dator och prova rensa cache/cookies i din webbläsare så bör det fungera.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@CamillaNYC Hello, if you wish to send us feedback regarding the experience with customer service please open a claim at https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Best regards,
Anton.

@_s1ld_ Hi, I'm sorry to hear that your flight was cancelled. We try to rebook you to the next available similar route to your original one but if you found a better alternative please contact us by phone for help with rebooking https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Dian1506 Hello Diana
I would advice you to not book separately. Either book 2 tickets with luggage included or 2 light tickets and you can add an extra luggage.
Kind regards /Anna

@_davidfallon Hello, I am sorry to hear you had a bad experience at LHR. I recommend that you send us feedback about this through our webform https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Best regards,
Anton.

@AstroArnberg Hello! Our live-chat function is working but the wait time might be longer than usual, we apologize for the inconvenience it is causing. Please contact us again via live-chat for help with your travel voucher questions.

Best regards,
Anton.

@CarlosMaradonna Hello, please contact us through Messenger or live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with more details and we will help you take a look at this.

Best regards,
Anton.

@snanail Hej Andreas 
Nej det är inget kännt fel just nu, prova att rensa din browser från historik och cookies. Vi kan hjälpa dig att boka om via telefon 0770 727 727 
Hälsningar /Anna

@ASkauen Hi, As a EuroBonus Gold and Diamond member you are welcome to use any Star Alliance member's lounge when traveling on a Star Alliance carrier operated flight.
https://t.co/kUgrAH65hn
Best regards /Anna

@LumiMoher Hej
Kontakta oss på live chat https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ eller på messenger så kan vi hjälpa dig med detta.
Vänliga hälsningar /Anna

@alanliv71828247 Hello,
I would like to ask you to contact our customer service and we will help you check your case. You will find our contact information on this page: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Regards Anja!

@foddiformsvacka Hej, om det gäller information och generella frågor så kan du kontakta oss via live-chatt eller Facebook Messenger. Om det gäller ett betalningsärende, ombokning eller nybokning så måste man ringa oss för hjälp med det.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@henrikbennetsen Hello Henrik, unfortunately we have no insight about the situation on CPH airport from here but I recommend you ask the airport personnel for more information about this.

Best regards,
Anton.

@peteyamr1 Hello, electronics must be transported in the carry-on bag. If the batteries can be taken out of the drone we recommend that you do that and tape the ends so they can not accidentally short-circuit.

Best regards,
Anton.

@heysamtucker Hi Sam 
When you upgrade it is the comfort and service on board that is upgraded , you can see the restrictions "The baggage allowance in your original ticket applies if you are upgraded" before you choose to upgrade https://t.co/lBHWsvX1tZ
Best regards /Anna

@MarcusKowal Hi Marcus
Please contact us on live chat or messenger https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj so we can help you further with this issue.
Kind regards/Anna

@NurseAndNomad Hi Susan 
Use this link https://t.co/gml5ZaEizi and scroll to "changes to our services " and you can see how food and beverages are now.
Kind regards /Anna

@Volatyle Hej, 
Via "mitt EuroBonus"&gt; inställningar&gt; kommunikation på https://t.co/83x76MtYnM  kan du hitta inställningar för hur du vill att vi kontaktar dig med exempelvis medlemserbjudanden. 

Tack för att du kontaktar oss, hälsningar Anja.

@malte Hello Malte, 
Please contact us and we will do our best to identify the problem. You will find our contact information here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Anja

@SquirtyBerti Hi Mambi
You will be contacted when your luggage has arrived, you can also check status via world tracer online with your PIR-number.

Kind regards /Anna

@polisa20 Hi Silje 
It is hard for me to answer , I do not know how the conversation went on phone. But as my colleague has answered , all available tickets and flights on webpage are scheduled to departure. 

Kind regards/Anna

@tyfusius Hej Geri
Telefon är +47 2189 6400 , vänta bara kvar så hamnar du i kö och får hjälp med ombokningen när det är din tur. (har du bokat via resebyrå vänligen kontakta dem)
Med vänliga hälsningar /Anna

@dsfrederik Hi Frederik 
You can try with another browser, otherwise you can request us to cancel via live chat , Facebook messenger or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj if you want to rebook you can only do it by phone not chat.
Kind regards /Anna

@RoberThompson13 Hi Rob
You can contact us on live chat or Facebook messenger if it is not regarding rebooking or payment, then you can call us https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards /Anna

@oliviayyli Hi Olivia
Please contact us on face book messenger or live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we can look at your refund.
Kind regards /Anna

@RobinCalmegard Hej Robin
Det går bra att boka ett datum för resa som är efter utgångsdatum, poängen förfaller om du bokar om eller bokar av resan efter att de har gått ut.
Med vänliga hälsningar /Anna

@TeenYogaGlobal Hello
I would advice you to call us if we may need to rebook you https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj we can not handle rebooking via Face book messenger.
Kind regards /Anna

@snowhenge Hi David
That transfer time should be OK but if any problems please contact staff at the airport.
Kind regards /Anna

@lovenjimmy Hej Jimmy
Om du har funderingar kring din bokning är du välkommen att kontakta oss på facebook messenger , live chat eller telefon https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ
Med vänliga hälsningar /Anna

@wojcik_russell Hello
You find the restrictions and what you can bring as carry if you klick on this link https://t.co/2UUXPRN2w1
Kind regards /Anna

@bunducafe Hello
In the SMS you should have an explanation why it is not confirmed, otherwise you can check at https://t.co/qN8gOdYYzJ
Kind regards /Anna

@kristoffbertram Hi! 

I'm sorry if your flight was changed, flights right now can be changed or cancelled due to the situation with Covid-19 but you can cancel the trip and get a full refund or contact our customer service to rebook the trip.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@brionycdavies Hi Briony
If all the flights in the booking are with SAS you can buy extra bag via this link https://t.co/D2hgbaFHcb ( if not you can only pay at the airport) i recommend google chrome it usually works good. Or you can book via phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards /Anna

@Charisimo Hello Kowa
You can find information regarding damaged baggage via this link https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM for further question please contact us on messenger, live chat or phone https://t.co/KQdOdrH9TM
Kind regards /Anna

@TeenYogaGlobal Hi TeenYoga
There has been some changes to the traffic program recently that has affected many flights. SMS or e-mail should been sent to the contact information in the booking. For any further questions please contact us on messenger and we will look at it.
Kind regards /Anna

@larskongshem Hi Lars
Yes, bad gateway usually is solved within a few minutes. Other errors is hard to answer about without specific information but we always recommend to clear browser or try with another browser/device to see if it solves the problem first.
Kind regards /Anna

@andreeamoprescu Hi Andreea
You can find information regarding corona and safe travel via this link https://t.co/E6bpHzaWLm
Kind regards/Anna

@scottey97 Hi scottey97
We follow the rules set by Transportstyrelsen so you can find what you can bring on board via this link https://t.co/0KTydnREF2 if any questions contact us by messenger.
Kind regards /Anna

@athenaragna Hi Athena 
Correct e-mail is identify.customer@sas.se to change phone number in euro bonus profile.
Kind regards /Anna

@JGuillaumee Hi Guillaume
Contact us on live messenger , live chat or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we can help you further.
Kind regards /Anna

@halelaiwa Hi jeje 
Yes it also applies when you pay with voucher. It will then be refunded to the same voucher.
Kind regards /Anna

@DigitalFairies Hello
I hope it solved at the airport. You can download boarding card via app, https://t.co/saQXo2wpQa "my bookings" or at the airport by self service automat or check in disk.
Kind regards/Anna

@halelaiwa Hi. The 24 hour full refund guarantee applies to all our tickets regardless of what payment option that is used to pay. If you book with a voucher and cancel within 24 hours the amount will be refunded back to the voucher.

Best regards,
Anton.

@xTemerz 2/2 For more information about current restrictions and changes to our service please visit https://t.co/gml5ZaEizi

With best regards,
Anton.
